 left corner. Useful for setting the desired frustum padding."], "extent": [4583, 4721]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "frameminimum"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Padding"], "extent": [4721, 4734], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Adds padding rotation (in degrees) to the camera to create a buffer between the focus object and the edge of the camera frustum."], "extent": [4755, 4901]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "padding"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 4, "text": ["Distribution Visualization"], "extent": [4901, 4938], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Camera Count"], "extent": [4938, 4957], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Specifies the number of points scattered to visualize potential camera placement locations (visualization only)."], "extent": [4979, 5109]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "camcount"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Point Color"], "extent": [5109, 5126], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Determines the color used to display the scattered points."], "extent": [5150, 5226]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "pointcolor"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Too Close Warning"], "extent": [5226, 5249], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Defines the color of points that are too close to the focus object, indicating that the object would exceed the camera\u2019s frustum."], "extent": [5278, 5418]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "tooclosewarning"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "examples", "container": true, "type": "examples_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [5418, 5428], "body": [{"type": "tip_gr